Uses of Class
edu.rit.numeric.Series

  • Packages that use Series 
    Package Description
    edu.rit.numeric
    Package edu.rit.numeric contains common classes for numerical computation.

    • Uses of Series in edu.rit.numeric

      Subclasses of Series in edu.rit.numeric 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ArraySeries
      Class ArraySeries provides a Series view of values stored in an array.
      class  ListSeries
      Class ListSeries provides a series of real values (type double); the series is variable-length.
      class  TransformedSeries
      Class TransformedSeries provides a Series that is formed by transforming the values in an underlying Series.
